WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:01.880
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:04.160
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:05.600
Well, praise the Lord.

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.760
You know, I've been getting all your letters.

00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:17.880
I got these pictures from a 15-year-old girl praying for her brother to come home to Jesus.

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:20.349
He's been wayward and he's not home.

00:00:21.340 --> 00:00:26.217
When I'm getting these letters, there are so many of them now that it's overwhelming.

00:00:26.217 --> 00:00:29.652
It's all the response to the pictures.

00:00:29.652 --> 00:00:45.840
I have so many pictures of people that are believing God for their unsaved loved ones and for their marriages—like this lady right here is praying for her marriage and for her hair to stop falling out because of the stress from the marriage stuff.

00:00:46.808 --> 00:00:50.680
I've got so many people.

00:00:51.800 --> 00:01:41.971
I thought, 'Man, if I could just train you all, if I could just impart to every single one of you how I've learned how to stand on the Word and get the Word down inside of me, so that you can do the same.

00:01:41.971 --> 00:01:59.275
' The Lord is no respecter of persons; it's about how big, how bad is your 'want-to.

00:01:59.275 --> 00:02:31.800
' As I'm agreeing with you and standing with you, the way you'll maintain it and keep it is by getting the Word down inside of your heart.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:38.965
I've seen people get many miracles.

00:02:38.965 --> 00:03:15.352
They get delivered from demonic spirits for a little season, but the Bible says the enemy comes back with seven more of his friends, worse than what he was, if they don't get the Word—if they find the house is empty.

00:03:28.359 --> 00:03:41.606
No matter how many times I pray for every single one of you and intercede, the buck stops with you ultimately.

00:03:44.547 --> 00:03:57.160
You will have to learn how to stand by faith and believe for your own stuff.

00:04:05.528 --> 00:04:13.040
The Bible says that you should know the truth and the truth will set you free.

00:04:13.040 --> 00:05:01.040
Now, I'm going to be your 'two' and I'm going to agree with you, but you have to get a foundation of the Word that is thick like concrete—so strong that when you build your house on it, you're not on the sinking sand or the quicksand.

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:13.813
You're on the solid Rock, and the Rock is the Word.

00:05:13.813 --> 00:05:24.588
You're going to hide that Word down in your heart.

00:05:24.588 --> 00:05:46.119
If you abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:05:46.119 --> 00:05:47.469
Period.

00:05:47.469 --> 00:05:55.417
So we're going to get the Word down inside our hearts.

00:05:55.417 --> 00:06:28.040
We're going to get the Word for every single person—all these prayer requests, all these people with wayward children, people saying they're battling with sexual perversions and homosexuality and wanting to be free from all these things.

00:06:28.969 --> 00:06:37.120
The Word has to be a priority, and there are no shortcuts.

00:06:37.120 --> 00:07:02.703
Regardless of what you're going through, there's nothing too big and there's nothing too small; the Word of God will change it all.

00:07:02.703 --> 00:07:06.639
Do you understand?

00:07:09.919 --> 00:07:17.980
The Word has to be the foundation in your life.

00:07:21.816 --> 00:07:29.947
You say, 'I don't understand the Word, I don't like reading the Word.

00:07:29.947 --> 00:07:41.599
' Find a version of the Bible that ministers to you.

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:48.859
Don't be religious; just get into the Word.

00:07:48.859 --> 00:07:56.850
Regardless of whatever it is, say, 'Hey, this speaks to me.

00:07:56.850 --> 00:08:16.340
' Find that and meditate on it continually, because you'll know the truth and the truth will set you free.

00:08:29.060 --> 00:08:46.455
No matter how many people say, 'I've got this going on over here, my daughter likes to play the Ouija board, she has tarot cards tattooed on her legs,' the devil's been defeated.

00:08:46.455 --> 00:09:01.479
The Lord is not going to do anything else about the devil; He defeated him.

00:09:01.479 --> 00:09:11.170
He triumphed over him, above all principalities and powers of might.

00:09:26.140 --> 00:09:33.449
He defeated the devil once and for all, and he's not going to go back and crucify himself again to deal with the devil again.

00:09:33.449 --> 00:09:34.499
Why?

00:09:34.499 --> 00:09:38.360
Because he's been defeated.

00:09:40.230 --> 00:09:47.560
He was victorious in every area: death, hell, and the grave.

00:09:50.820 --> 00:09:54.160
He triumphed over poverty, lack, sickness, and disease.

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:55.225
Everything.

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:03.609
He won once and for all; it's already done.

00:10:03.609 --> 00:10:24.848
So your devil problem is you not standing on the authority of the believer and telling the devil he has no right or place in your house.

00:10:24.848 --> 00:10:26.893
Take your authority.

00:10:26.893 --> 00:10:32.360
Take communion—grape juice or whatever you have—daily.

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:39.143
Take the anointing oil and anoint your house.

00:10:39.143 --> 00:10:51.320
I got this oil from some sister in the Lord and it smells like frankincense.

00:10:58.456 --> 00:11:01.450
You can get it on Amazon and anoint your house.

00:11:01.450 --> 00:11:11.280
Go around and anoint your kids with oil.

00:11:18.850 --> 00:11:38.107
I put a bloodline on my kids; I anoint my windows just like the children of Israel did when the death angel passed.

00:11:38.107 --> 00:11:59.800
They put the lamb's blood upon the door, and the death angel was not allowed to come in and kill, steal, or destroy.

00:12:03.090 --> 00:12:33.480
You apply the blood over your house by olive oil or whatever you have and pray, 'Father, this represents your blood, and I apply this blood over the doorpost of my house, my bed, my husband, and my wife.

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:53.020
' We're going to stand on the Word and not allow the devil to come in like a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:12:53.020 --> 00:12:57.660
That means he can't devour everybody.

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:08.710
The ones he can't devour are the ones that have the blood applied upon them.

00:13:08.710 --> 00:13:16.186
He cannot devour a blood-washed, born-again Christian.

00:13:16.186 --> 00:13:31.724
I believe with all my heart there's power and authority in the name of Jesus and the blood of Jesus.

00:13:31.724 --> 00:13:47.610
So you must understand your covenant and plead the blood over your unsaved loved ones.

00:13:47.610 --> 00:14:28.160
Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever, so this is what I'm going to tell you to do: say, according to Ephesians, 'May the eyes of their understanding be enlightened, Holy Spirit, and flood their eyes with light that they would know the hope of their calling.

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:44.866
' Saul had a Damascus road experience with the Lord that shook him from the inside out.

00:14:44.866 --> 00:15:04.828
He was blinded for those three days and he was healed, and the Lord set him on the course because God had a plan for his life.

00:15:04.828 --> 00:15:15.639
No matter how much evil he did, God showed up and showed off in his life.

00:15:16.159 --> 00:15:31.709
I believe that there's no one too far gone for Jesus to save.

00:15:31.709 --> 00:15:58.691
They may be the biggest murderer or the biggest idolater, but God can take them out of that pit of despair and turn their life around within just a second.

00:15:58.691 --> 00:16:05.782
Once you're gone and you're dead, it's over—TKO.

00:16:08.773 --> 00:16:21.435
But no matter how far you think your unsaved loved ones are, it only takes one second.

00:16:21.435 --> 00:16:39.020
I've seen the worst of the worst sinners when I worked for Victory Church in Oklahoma City.

00:16:43.639 --> 00:16:56.871
I saw people that you would think have no hope turn around within just a couple of days.

00:17:05.280 --> 00:17:23.949
I remember one guy who had planned out his suicide—had the weapon and everything hidden—and was coming to church for the last time before he did himself in.

00:17:38.253 --> 00:17:51.170
The power of God hit him in the middle of the church service and he gave his heart to Jesus Christ that day.

00:17:51.170 --> 00:18:14.750
He told his wife, 'I was ready to do myself in,' but he got radically born again and started serving at the church.

00:18:14.750 --> 00:18:33.714
My point is that there's an expiration date, but there is a way to believe for every single one of these.

00:18:39.219 --> 00:18:57.818
The Lord said, 'Brandon, the only way they know is by you teaching them, because you're not getting a lot of it from your churches.

00:18:57.818 --> 00:19:13.240
' A lot of pastors are teaching a lukewarm word—a 30-minute sermonette.

00:19:19.995 --> 00:19:45.159
You may get a worship service with jammed-out music, fog machines, and lights, but you walk away still empty, wondering, 'What about my issues?

00:19:45.159 --> 00:19:50.040
What about my wayward child?

00:19:50.040 --> 00:19:56.707
What about the diagnosis from the doctor?

00:19:56.707 --> 00:20:12.008
' I'm telling you how you're going to do it when the rubber meets the road: you stand.

00:20:12.008 --> 00:20:14.840
Stand therefore!

00:20:14.840 --> 00:20:45.056
When you get the Word down in your heart, it becomes a weapon, and you speak that Word out of your mouth because life and death are in the power of your tongue.

00:20:51.290 --> 00:21:02.460
What you are saying every time you come up against your circumstances is what you're going to be facing tomorrow.

00:21:16.186 --> 00:21:17.774
Your words either make you or break you.

00:21:17.774 --> 00:21:18.750
Seriously.

00:21:20.760 --> 00:21:32.770
You go around saying, 'My marriage is terrible,' and you're living exactly what you said.

00:21:38.025 --> 00:21:44.510
But you start saying, 'I'm not moved by what I see or feel.

00:21:50.468 --> 00:21:51.314
I'm moved by what the Word says.

00:21:51.314 --> 00:22:00.009
' Think on things that are lovely and of a good report.

00:22:00.009 --> 00:22:06.011
As the mind goes, the man follows.

00:22:06.011 --> 00:22:16.120
You're snared by the words of your mouth; that's what the Bible says.

00:22:16.120 --> 00:22:29.240
So we've got to change the way we think, because out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:33.400
Your mountain has to hear your voice!

00:22:33.400 --> 00:22:38.964
You have to say it over and over again.

00:22:38.964 --> 00:22:44.155
It's the consistency—like a hammer hitting a rock.

00:22:44.155 --> 00:22:56.770
How long have you been speaking to your circumstances saying, 'We're never going to get out of this'?

00:22:56.770 --> 00:22:59.429
'Grandma was poor, we were poor.

00:22:59.429 --> 00:23:02.695
' That's what you're living.

00:23:02.695 --> 00:23:09.679
But Christ redeemed you from the curse of the law.

00:23:09.679 --> 00:23:22.415
Galatians says Christ has redeemed me from the curse of the law, and generational curses are a curse.

00:23:22.415 --> 00:23:33.853
I'm not under the curse, and a curse without a cause cannot stand.

00:23:33.853 --> 00:23:47.865
I anoint myself with oil and I believe in my covenant.

00:24:00.964 --> 00:24:08.040
I say, 'God, you're going to get me out of this because you've already paid the price for it.

00:24:08.040 --> 00:24:17.295
' Father, you said by your stripes I am healed, regardless of what my flesh says.

00:24:17.295 --> 00:24:35.582
I'm redeemed from the curse of the law; I'm not going to have heart disease or diabetes because I set the standard.

00:24:44.520 --> 00:24:48.793
The Word says that I'm free, and whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:24:48.793 --> 00:25:02.853
Who is this uncircumcised Philistine that you should try to defy the armies of the living God?

00:25:03.787 --> 00:25:15.427
I will go and slay this giant and cut his head off!

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:24.559
My God is bigger than cancer, a bad marriage, or a wayward child.

00:25:24.559 --> 00:25:37.559
He's able to do exceedingly, abundantly above all that I dare ask or think.

00:25:37.559 --> 00:25:43.269
Today is your day.

00:25:55.051 --> 00:26:04.234
You have to believe with your heart and confess with your mouth that Jesus Christ is Lord.

00:26:04.234 --> 00:26:18.120
That's how you got saved, and it's the same way I believe for everything else.

00:26:18.120 --> 00:26:20.764
Today I'm free.

00:26:21.182 --> 00:26:56.640
I will not have night terrors or PTSD, because he was wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities; the chastisement of our peace was upon him, and with his stripes we are healed.

00:26:56.640 --> 00:27:16.159
God has not given me a spirit of fear, but of power, of love, and of a sound mind.

00:27:31.399 --> 00:27:31.609
I refuse not to have a balanced mind because he's already given me peace.

00:27:31.609 --> 00:27:40.314
It's a free gift; I receive it.

00:27:54.440 --> 00:27:56.785
Jesus paid the price for me to walk in victory in every area of my life.

00:28:08.720 --> 00:28:08.953
Every believer has been given a measure of faith.

00:28:11.687 --> 00:28:29.000
I am not favored any more than you are; I've just been more obedient and decided to ground my feet and say, 'I'm not moved.

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:38.240
' How bad do you want your circumstances to change?

00:28:38.240 --> 00:28:40.869
There's no shortcuts.

00:28:46.704 --> 00:28:59.600
You can go to the gym and look amazing, or you can eat and be heavy like me—I'm just being real with y'all.

00:29:04.355 --> 00:29:09.608
I work my spirit out all the time in the spiritual gym.

00:29:09.608 --> 00:29:30.137
Diana said, 'Brandon, there's a difference between people who are desperate for change versus people who just want it handed to them.

00:29:30.137 --> 00:29:40.304
' There's no welfare system in the spirit realm.

00:29:40.304 --> 00:29:55.380
Welfare is good for a season if you need it, but you can't live there.

00:29:55.380 --> 00:30:20.359
There are seasons of grace where God will spoon-feed you as a baby, but when you become a spiritual adult, it's like that eagle that kicks her eaglets out of the nest.

00:30:31.425 --> 00:30:35.133
It's time for you to flap your wings and fly, or you're going to die.

00:30:35.133 --> 00:30:42.312
No more of this pacifier Christianity stuff.

00:30:42.312 --> 00:30:50.606
We've got to put on our armor.

00:30:50.606 --> 00:30:54.200
Either you put on the armor or he's going to devour you.

00:30:54.200 --> 00:31:00.559
He'll keep poking you until you say enough's enough.

00:31:00.559 --> 00:31:15.195
I heard about a bully in school writing down the names of people he thought he could whip.

00:31:15.195 --> 00:31:16.786
This is the devil.

00:31:16.786 --> 00:31:26.250
A kid saw his name on that list and said, 'You can't whip me!

00:31:26.250 --> 00:31:31.076
Take my name off that list.

00:31:31.076 --> 00:31:41.186
Greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world.

00:31:41.186 --> 00:31:43.533
' Guess what?

00:31:43.533 --> 00:31:46.550
That bully erased the name.

00:31:46.550 --> 00:31:51.879
That's what you've got to do.

00:31:51.879 --> 00:31:57.360
You're not doing this alone.

00:31:57.360 --> 00:32:06.469
Christ in you is the hope of glory.

00:32:12.720 --> 00:32:14.600
That's why we take communion, because we have a covenant.

00:32:25.639 --> 00:32:28.576
I choose to believe in the power and authority of the blood of Jesus over my kids.

00:32:28.576 --> 00:32:39.999
Make much of the blood, and the blood will make much of you.

00:32:39.999 --> 00:32:58.188
So we lift up this body and we believe that he became sickness for us; this is the meal that heals.

00:32:58.188 --> 00:33:04.211
Father, I believe you're the Healer.

00:33:04.211 --> 00:33:16.073
I thank you that my sins are washed in your blood.

00:33:16.073 --> 00:33:36.650
No generational curse is bigger than the blood of Jesus, no matter how big it is in your mind.

00:33:36.650 --> 00:33:42.320
Find scriptures that pertain to what you're believing God for.

00:33:42.320 --> 00:33:57.259
If you can't sleep, the Bible says he gives his beloved sweet, restful sleep.

00:34:07.188 --> 00:34:09.067
The Word will work if you work it.

00:34:09.067 --> 00:34:23.595
Father, right now in the name of Jesus, I believe for every single photo.

00:34:23.595 --> 00:34:40.274
This South Korean family is believing for their family members; we're believing that false religion is broken off of these families.

00:34:42.119 --> 00:34:49.990
I agree with them right now that they are delivered from satanic bondage.

00:34:51.800 --> 00:35:00.288
We believe marriages are strong and her hair stops falling out.

00:35:01.1000 --> 00:35:06.498
I call her brother home in Jesus' name.

00:35:17.186 --> 00:35:22.240
I call all the cancer patients and this young man bound by homosexuality free in the name of Jesus.

00:35:22.240 --> 00:35:27.040
Visit them in the midnight hour.

00:35:27.040 --> 00:35:34.320
No one's too far gone.

00:35:49.366 --> 00:35:49.977
Receive your miracle in Jesus' name.

00:35:49.977 --> 00:35:58.599
We pray for Nicole and her husband.

00:35:58.599 --> 00:36:09.555
We thank you for better jobs for Tommy and favor with the court systems.

00:36:09.555 --> 00:36:28.773
For those who have lost their children to the DHS system, let them get right and be good parents.

00:36:28.773 --> 00:36:42.839
They just made some bad choices, but they changed their reprobate minds by the Word of God.

00:36:42.839 --> 00:36:54.657
It's the only thing that will ever set you completely free.

00:36:54.657 --> 00:37:09.095
You'll never stay free without the Word because the devil comes immediately to challenge it.

00:37:09.095 --> 00:37:14.440
He knows your weak spots.

00:37:17.662 --> 00:37:28.854
You've got to speak it out your mouth: 'Get out of here in Jesus' name!

00:37:28.854 --> 00:37:42.820
' Submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:37:53.833 --> 00:37:54.044
Jesus was tempted on everything, but he resisted steadfast.

00:37:54.044 --> 00:37:59.103
I'm not going down that road again.

00:37:59.103 --> 00:38:08.599
I'm not looking at filth on the internet; I made a covenant with my eyes.

00:38:21.468 --> 00:38:21.824
I refuse to submit to the devil.

00:38:21.824 --> 00:38:25.055
Enough is enough.

00:38:37.177 --> 00:38:37.611
We don't hate people; we love them and tell them the truth.

00:38:37.611 --> 00:38:43.620
Many are one breath away from eternity.

00:38:43.620 --> 00:38:57.244
The spirit realm is more real than your skin, but many play with fire—adultery and all these things.

00:38:57.244 --> 00:39:00.811
Father, I thank you for revival.

00:39:00.811 --> 00:39:07.080
We walk in victory, going from glory to glory.

00:39:09.942 --> 00:39:18.119
I refuse to keep being the same; I want to come up higher with the fire.

00:39:22.160 --> 00:39:24.100
Those who seek me will find me.

00:39:24.400 --> 00:39:29.300
I want that burning bush experience!

00:39:29.300 --> 00:39:34.306
Father, we receive our freedom today.

00:39:34.306 --> 00:39:45.029
Thank you, Lord, that Megan is healed and we're walking in health.

00:39:45.029 --> 00:39:50.400
We have the mind of Christ.

00:39:50.400 --> 00:39:54.296
Better days are ahead of us.

00:40:05.960 --> 00:40:08.600
My marriage is strong and blessed; we'll never taste divorce or adultery.

00:40:08.600 --> 00:40:16.600
You've got to believe it and speak to your mountain.

00:40:16.600 --> 00:40:21.040
Father, I thank you.

00:40:34.902 --> 00:40:38.400
I bind the spirit of strife in the name of Jesus and I command you to cease and desist.

00:40:38.400 --> 00:40:57.850
Go in the bathroom or the laundry room and say, 'I bind the spirit of lust and pornography out of my house.

00:41:05.079 --> 00:41:05.359
I bind anger and abuse.

00:41:05.359 --> 00:41:16.017
' You take authority over that devil.

00:41:16.017 --> 00:41:23.840
I bind that spirit of rebellion in my kids.

00:41:23.840 --> 00:41:30.549
Check what your kids are listening to and watching.

00:41:30.549 --> 00:41:33.744
Garbage in, garbage out.

00:41:33.744 --> 00:41:41.996
We will not have a spirit of rebellion in my house.

00:41:41.996 --> 00:41:47.359
Spare the rod, spoil the child.

00:41:50.786 --> 00:41:51.275
God corrects those he loves.

00:41:51.275 --> 00:41:58.090
I've even gotten spankings from the Holy Ghost before.

00:41:58.090 --> 00:42:08.190
There seems to be a topic inside of my spirit.

00:42:08.190 --> 00:42:12.880
Say it; say it again.

00:42:12.880 --> 00:42:27.263
God corrects those he loves because he has an amazing plan for your life.

00:42:27.263 --> 00:42:33.280
I want to live on the victory side.

00:42:33.280 --> 00:42:42.813
Faith comes by hearing the Word of God.

00:42:48.368 --> 00:42:50.072
We bless every person here in the name of Jesus.

00:42:50.072 --> 00:42:50.964
Amen.

00:42:50.964 --> 00:42:56.733
Well, I want to see you victorious.

00:43:00.893 --> 00:43:13.916
If you liked this video, please like and subscribe; it helps us in the algorithm.

00:43:18.863 --> 00:43:19.131
I want you to stay free.

00:43:19.131 --> 00:43:27.036
The Word works if you work it.

00:43:27.036 --> 00:43:32.040
Get your spirit man fat and fluffy on the Word of God.

00:43:32.040 --> 00:43:37.760
Put a smile on your face and a song on your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
